{"tid":928000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘭桂坊男女旁若無人 街頭真人騷","createTime":"2018-12-04T14:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T14:07:04.000Z","uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7aba0725cb636d6732951e94b225ee66ced5d7bf","tid":928000,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"蘭桂坊男女旁若無人 街頭真人騷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543913137_fc23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543913137_fc23.jpg&h=fae823ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 一對男女周一凌晨時份在蘭桂坊當街纏綸，吸引路人圍觀拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543913418_d555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543913418_d555.jpg&h=4119a77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事男女旁若無人當街纏綿，外籍女更坐在男伴身上，不斷郁動身體。<br />\n<br />\n蘭桂坊上演真人騷？市民錢先生周一凌晨1點幾，行經中環蘭桂坊德己立街娛樂行商場對開，就見到成班人圍住一間店舖玻璃櫥窗係咁笑，就好奇咁走去睇吓乜事啦，點知就見到一對年約30零歲嘅外籍女同華裔男子坐喺度激戰，他形容當時女上男下，戰情相當激烈，兩人都十分忘我咁。<br />\n<br />\n錢生話當時嗰對男女慾火焚身，外籍女坐喺男伴身上狂嘴對方，身體又不停上下郁動，男伴都唔弱，當街伸手入女方衣衫內不停游走。<br />\n<br />\n阿錢生話，呢對男女當街纏綿咗5分鐘，圍觀嘅人越嚟越多，有人開始拍片、仲一邊影一邊笑，又有人吱吱斟，之後嗰對男女終於發現自己成為焦點，就好匆忙咁整理衣衫，然後互相扶對方起身走向港鐵站匆匆離開。錢生話兩人離去時腳步浮浮，應該飲咗唔少酒，估計都係酒後亂性累事啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181204/58991439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58991439&d=PVI6hBKaofi%2BzSQIbQ7rMEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=21400d82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58991439&h=9f933746\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181204/58991439</a>"},{"pid":"62914f859e04c0e2bcbd8a623df69aba075b24bb","tid":928000,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/d85/d1e/d85d1ed07a5b5bcc018aeab9a932ed205724d98d_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fd85%2Fd1e%2Fd85d1ed07a5b5bcc018aeab9a932ed205724d98d_n.jpg&h=0c63db07&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}